         <abstract>
            <p>The ideal CALL courseware development procedure will take advantage of many or all of the latest hardware, pedagogical, and theoretical advances in the language teaching field. These advances are presented in this paper both as a description of the ideal CALL courseware and, where applicable, as actual design implementations in a Spanish course being developed by the author.</p>
